By Ex-Minister Ayelet Shaked
Please share!

On Thursday I received a phone call from Avichai, who told me how his wife and their three small children had been kidnapped by Hamas to Gaza.

When the call ended, I couldn’t stop the tears.

But crying is not an action plan. This video needs to reach every corner of the world, every decision-maker, official and influencer who can help, each and every person who can add their voice.

#HamasisISIS

Please watch till the end , shows exactly the two sides . Please share - this past Thursday while Jews and Israelis were silently rallying for Israel at Columbia university , there was a Pro Hamas demonstration singing “ free Palestine - from the river to the sea”

London. 
Christmas Day. 
Your home 
What if it were you?
I think the world is finally starting to  understand
Mia, Adam, Alex, Michael’s dad. 🇮🇱🏳️‍🌈 Diamonds, Jewelry, Fitness , Kids Co-Founder @minty.nyc
